blogPost.excerpt:
ET's Melicia Johnson spoke with Tessica Brown, who gives an update on the status of her hair after making the mistake of styling it with Gorilla Glue. Tessica opened up about her video of the aftermath going viral and how the sudden fame is affecting her, and she also reveals the celebrities who have reached out to offer their assistance.

Exclusives from #ETonline :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQwITQ__CeH2Y_7g2xeiNDa0vQsROQQgv

localize.title: Tessica Brown希望自己永远不要发布大猩猩胶水视频。她对互联网的留言（独家
localize.description:
ET的梅利西亚-约翰逊（Melicia Johnson）采访了泰西卡-布朗（Tessica Brown），她给出了她用Gorilla胶水做造型的错误后的最新状态。Tessica公开了她的事后视频被传播，以及突如其来的名气对她的影响，她还透露了那些伸出援手的名人。

独家报道来自#ETonline 。

ET的梅利西亞-約翰遜（Melicia Johnson）採訪了泰西卡-布朗（Tessica Brown），她給出了她用Gorilla膠水做造型的錯誤後的最新狀態。Tessica公開了她的事後視頻被傳播，以及突如其來的名氣對她的影響，她還透露了那些伸出援手的名人。
